<h2>Our Removal Process</h2>
<ol style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.7);padding-left:20px;line-height:2.2">
<li><strong>Vehicle inspection</strong> — assess wrap age, vinyl type, and paint condition</li>
<li><strong>Controlled heating</strong> — infrared heat softens adhesive for clean release</li>
<li><strong>Slow peeling</strong> — vinyl removed at optimal angle to prevent paint pull</li>
<li><strong>Adhesive removal</strong> — citrus-based cleaners dissolve residue without damaging clear coat</li>
<li><strong>Surface inspection</strong> — verify paint condition and prep for re-wrap if applicable</li>
<li><strong>Delivery</strong> — vehicle returned clean and wrap-free</li>
</ol>
