<li><strong>Lease return</strong> — vehicle must be returned in original condition</li>
<li><strong>Design update</strong> — refreshing fleet graphics with a new look</li>
<li><strong>Vehicle sale</strong> — removing graphics before selling or trading in</li>
<li><strong>Wrap age</strong> — vinyl is past its rated life and beginning to show wear</li>
<li><strong>Damage repair</strong> — body work requires wrap removal before paint repair</li>
</ul>
